metadata.name: unPOP! #1/6
metadata.description: unPOP! is made from bits of Eduardo Paolozziâ€™s series of collages, made between 1947 and 1952, called Bunk! Containing cuttings from comics and magazines featuring cartoon characters, film stars, adverts, logos and burlesque pin-ups, these collages were instrumental in the creation of the cultural identity of the pop art movement.
